    <mxCell id="33" value="/                     → Dashboard (protected)&lt;br&gt;/journal              → Journal (protected)&lt;br&gt;/settings             → Settings (protected)&lt;br&gt;/admin                → AdminPanel (protected + is_admin)&lt;br&gt;/onboarding           → Onboarding (public)&lt;br&gt;/way-to-goal          → WayToGoal (public)&lt;br&gt;/tariffs              → Tariffs (public)&lt;br&gt;/auth                 → AuthScreen (public)&lt;br&gt;/auth/google/callback → Google OAuth callback&lt;br&gt;/auth/apple/callback  → Apple OAuth callback&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AuthGuard:&lt;br&gt;  401 → /onboarding&lt;br&gt;  !onboarding_completed → /onboarding&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;DeepLink (app_links):&lt;br&gt;  app.kayfit.ru/* → открыть приложение&lt;br&gt;  t.me bot callback → /auth?token=...&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Domain routing:&lt;br&gt;  kayfit.ru → Landing (web-only)&lt;br&gt;  app.kayfit.ru → Flutter app" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
